Eu sou o Sin Siwat Merton.

00:45:47.077 --> 00:45:47.898
Merton?

00:45:50.237 --> 00:45:51.397
O seu pai é...

00:45:51.997 --> 00:45:52.797
Bem...

00:45:53.037 --> 00:45:55.277
